resources: PlantIdentifier Welcome! Do you often see plants and wish you knew what they were? This app is for you! \"Identify Plants\" will prompt you to choose a photo of a plant from your phone. You will then know what your plant is and have the opportunity to look up more information about it. Enjoy! Identify plants!
